{
  "texts": [
    "Results and Ablation studyWe analyzed the contributions to our final results of different components of the data augmentation policy (Table 2) and modification of the event processing method or model architecture (Table 3).",
    "We report both the accuracy, with a 10-pixel error allowed (i.e.",
    "p10), and the average distance in pixels from ground-truth.",
    "Note that the values reported in this section are calculated on the validation set as defined in the challenge's original code repository.",
    "From Table 2, we see that performing spatial affine augmentation of the event data provided boosted the performance of our model by 0.375."
  ]
